      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Task Status</h2>

  <p>Default statuses:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Todo</strong> - Not started</li>
    <li><strong>In Progress</strong> - Currently being worked on</li>
    <li><strong>Done</strong> - Completed</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Change status by:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Clicking the status badge and selecting a new status</li>
    <li>Dragging the task in Board view</li>
    <li>Using keyboard shortcut <code>S</code> then selecting</li>
    <li>Via API or CLI</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Board View (Kanban)</h2>

  <p>
    The board view shows tasks as cards organized by status columns. Drag cards between columns to update status.
  </p>

  <h2>Filtering & Search</h2>

  <p>Filter tasks by:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Status</li>
    <li>Assignee</li>
    <li>Priority</li>
    <li>Labels</li>
    <li>Due date range</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Use the search bar to find tasks by title or description content.</p>

